name: Apple
desc: Apples are an incredibly nutritious fruit that offers multiple health benefits

name: Banana
desc: One to two bananas per day is considered a moderate intake for most healthy people.

name: Coconut
desc: Give you better oral health. The MCFAs found in coconut meat also contain antimicrobial properties.

name: Guava
desc: Guava is bursting with Vitamin C, which is critical for maintaining immune health.

name: Grapes
desc: Studies have shown that eating grapes doesn't just support your physical health, but also your cognitive health,

name: Mango
desc: Mango is one of the sweetest fruits and lower in fiber than other fruits, so a good rule of thumb is not to exceed two servings a day.
